      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOVE IS GONE (5) stuck on well last time to finish 0.8 lengths back in second (19.58) at this track in a Other over 340m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can go on with it. INDY GRANT (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.28 beating Mini Mara. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from five starts. Can make it two on the bounce. POP'S GIRL (6) turned in a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 340m behind Trick (20.08) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Has ability and can measure up. UNLIKELY DANGER (1) is a last-start placegetter who will have admirers.",
